be.belgium.eid.objects
Class IDAddress

java.lang.Object
  be.belgium.eid.objects.IDAddress
All Implemented Interfaces:
SmartCardReadable
public class IDAddress
extends java.lang.Object
implements SmartCardReadable

The IDAddress class represents the address of the holder of the current beID card. It includes the street, zip code and municipality.

Version:
1.0.0 08 Dec 2007
Author:
Kristof Overdulve
